{"tid":1420568,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[敵人反對的就做對了]對準警察記者會","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:31:18.000Z","uid":156843,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d999bb0b2d7379d5b0fdffc61e6b1ca1bbc6b4a9","tid":1420568,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"林鄭記招後，政府指每日都會開記者會交代局勢，心水清嘅巴打都知咩料<br />\n接住周保松老師〈論林鄭的新論述〉同劉細良係城寨都提到，<br />\n政府係想為事件<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重新定性</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放大社會亂局，令原本轉色嘅淺藍歸隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嚟到今日民間記者會嘅時候，記者一直就相關問題提問<br />\n1. 放大示威者過火<br />\n2. 指記者會無代表性<br />\n<br />\n睇得出政府係好驚，極度想將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利用社會亂局去驅散民意</span></span>，亦都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好驚我地團結咁去發聲</span></span>，令到佢地無得一言堂<br />\n(佢一定無想像過無大台，都會搞到發聲平台去抗衡佢個記者會，多謝巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n所以，要令警察個記者會失效，一定要：<br />\n1. 利用文宣，針對記者會失實、抹黑嘅言論，逐點擊破<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 廣傳比身邊嘅淺藍聽，警察記者＝大話發佈會，令佢地潛意識都會質疑咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛主席都教大家：「如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港！<br />\n時化革命！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"814b88624a54ed8d3ce8bbb5c350145c4c807bf7","tid":1420568,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2c85c330f16d3c6722b9d42a8d703790fc02b4","tid":1420568,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"28ddfc6067c055431a62c56e760fe9bcf0d9279d","tid":1420568,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞬間沉底"},{"pid":"848c721881fee925d4ffce14ba5f5d8c3c3a58aa","tid":1420568,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"係時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">代</span></strong></span>革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc279410a67cc2731e35e0fb9e86d9d54a74417","tid":1420568,"uid":174319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"偉大的毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6128359eae2c660b893509b667272e2e06cc18","tid":1420568,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"繼「不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆」同埋Be Water後抗爭新原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420765</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d21ba505c441f3e0f68007792750469eeac4d7aa","tid":1420568,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}